- Show the current month calendar with current day highlighted
- Provide dropdown to select month and year (2000-2050)
- On selection of month/ year, display the dates accordingly
- On click of a date, set as start date
- On click of second date, set as end date
- Validate end date > start date
- Highlight selected range

Bonus features

- On selection of third date, reset range and start fresh
- Allow selection of multiple dates, without range (eg, 21/4, 24/4, 25/4)
